Jo-Israel ikore mondo omonj piny Kanaan


1  Kane Musa jatich Ruoth Nyasaye osetho, Ruoth Nyasaye nowacho ni Joshua wuod Nun, mane jalup Musa niya, 
2  “Musa jatichna osetho. Omiyo ikri gi jo-Israel duto mondo ung’ad aora Jordan, udhi e piny mamiyou. 
3  

Kamoro amora ma tiendu onyono, nobed maru, kaka nasingora ni Musa. 
4  Kuonde duto nobed mau, chakre e thim ma yo milambo, nyaka Lebanon yo nyandwat, kendo koa Yufrate, aora maduong’ man yo wuok chieng’, koluwo piny jo-Hiti, nyaka Nam Mediterenia man yo podho chieng’. 
5  

Onge ng’at ma nosiri nyaka chieng’. Anabed kodi kaka nabet gi Musa, Ok naweyi kata jwang’i ok najwang’i. 
6  

Bed gi chir, kendo gi jing’o, nimar in ema nitel ni jogagi, ka gikawo piny mane asingora ni kweregi ni namigi. 
7  To bed mana gi chir, kendo gi jing’o, kiluwo chik duto mane Musa jatichna omiyi. Kik iwe chikno, kibaro koracham kata korachwich, mi inibed gi hawi kuonde duto midhiye. 
8  Kik wiyi wil gi Kitap Chikno, to nyaka isome odiechieng’ gotieno, kendo ine ni iluwo chik duto mondikie. Eka inidongi, kendo noguedh gik moko duto mitimo. 
9  Par kaka asechiki ni mondo ibed gi chir kendo gi jing’o. Kik iluor, kendo kik chunyi nyosre, nikech an Ruoth Nyasaye ma Nyasachi, an kodi kuonde duto midhiye.”


10  Eka Joshua nochiko jotend jo-Israel kowachonigi niya, 
11  “Wuothuru e kambi duto, kunyiso ji niya, ‘Ikreuru, nimar bang’ ndalo adek ubiro ng’ado aora Jordan, mondo ukaw piny ma Ruoth Nyasaye miyou.’ ”


12  

Joshua nowacho ni jo-Reuben gi jo-Gad kod jo-Manase konchiel niya, 
13  “Paruru gima Musa jatich Ruoth Nyasaye nochikou, kowacho niya, ‘Ruoth Nyasaye ma Nyasachu nomiu pinyni mondo obed kar daku.’ 
14  Mondu gi nyithindu kod jambu nyalo dong’ e piny mane Musa omiyou yo wuok chieng’ mar aora Jordan, to un jolweny nyaka uidh loka, kutelo e nyim jo-Israel weteu, mondo ukonygi kedo. 
15  Ka gin bende gisekawo piny ma Ruoth Nyasaye ma Nyasachu miyogi, kendo gidakie, eka unuduogi, mondo udag e pinyu uwegi man yo wuok chieng mar aora Jordan, mane Musa jatich Nyasaye omiyou.”


16  Ne giduoko Joshua niya, “Wanatim duto michikowa, kendo wanadhi kamoro amora miorowae. 
17  Wanawinji kaka ne wawinjo Musa, to Nyasaye mondo obed kodi kaka nobedo gi Musa! 
18  Ng’ato ang’ata ma nodagi winjo chikni, kata ma notamre timo gima ichiko, nonegi. Omiyo bed gi chir kendo gi jing’o!”

